{"about_the_game":"Developed by INGAME, the war-themed game DeathGearX has been released on the Microsoft Store! As a rising star in the mech game genre, it has garnered significant attention by perfectly blending TPS (third-person shooter) and RTS (real-time strategy) elements. Here, you can experience the allure of mechs, upgrade your favorite vehicles, and pilot your custom-built war machines to conquer the battlefield!<br />\r\nDeathGearX is a war-themed game that combines the characteristics of both TPS and RTS genres. In the game, you can collect numerous vehicles, including tanks, robots, and jeeps, and engage in fierce battles by upgrading and modifying these large weapons. You can also enjoy the thrill of real-time multiplayer battles, experiencing the intense and brutal battlefield! Moreover, you can team up with friends, fighting side by side to dominate the battlefield together!<br />\r\nThe story is set in the near future, where advancements in human technology have led to widespread use of AI in military applications. Unfortunately, a malfunction in some AI defense units caused them to attack civilians indiscriminately, sparking a war between AI forces and humans. In the game, you start with a basic vehicle, which you can transform into an unparalleled war machine through upgrades and modifications as your skills and resources grow. You will need to pilot this vehicle, lead your troops, and fight against the formidable AI army to save the human world.<br />\r\nAs you progress through the game, you will acquire more vehicles to enhance your arsenal and gather sufficient resources to upgrade your vehicles to face the ever-changing, brutal battlefield.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3054070?t=1723087810","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054070/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1723087810","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a